MysticView class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "AreaClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  MysticView class is a subclass of Area class and it is used to
  display picture files via mysticview.library.

  MysticView is a subclass of MysticView.mcc so you must have
  MysticView.mcc in MUI:Libs/MUI to use it. MysticView.mcc is
  copyright of Steve Quartly.

  Bug: If you send a ctrl_c to a macro running a MysticView
  object that is loading its pictures, the application freezes.
  That is a MysticView.mcc bug.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

